DESCRIPTION >
    Get daily search volume over time. Returns date and count of searches per day. Perfect for line or area charts showing search trends. Use days_back parameter (default 30) to control the time range.

NODE searches_by_day_data
SQL >
    %
    SELECT
        toDate(timestamp) as date,
        count() as count
    FROM events
    WHERE timestamp >= now() - INTERVAL {{Int32(days_back, 30)}} DAY
    GROUP BY date
    ORDER BY date

TYPE endpoint